een them is still impossible. Given that Leopoldo’s body hasn’t appeared, Hilario decides to go to the city to tell Fernanda that Federico accidentally shot her father; her reaction causes her to faint. Eugenia, worried because she senses that something bad is happening, leaves a message for Leopoldo on his phone telling him how much she loves him. Nicolas is discouraged because he hasn’t found Leopoldo, but Florencia encourages him to keep the faith that he will find him. Federico gets scared when Moncho and another henchman want to forcibly remove him from the room where he is staying." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="3089000" grandparentArt="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentRatingKey="67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentThumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg" grandparentTitle="La Trepadora" grandparentType="show" index="56" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" title="S01:E056" userState="0"><Image alt="S01:E056" type="coverArt" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E056" type="coverPoster" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E056" type="snapshot" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1776950196" duration="3089000" endsAt="1776953285" id="69e18014cf9964ca16f72387" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776980060" duration="3088000" endsAt="1776983148" id="69e18014cf9964ca16f72391" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="